articles.title: Investigation of exercise-mimetic bioactive molecules as modulators of MMP activity and expression in cancer cells.
articles.summary:
Here's a clear, concise summary in under 25 words:

Specific exercise-mimetic molecules can inhibit key proteins involved in lung cancer cell growth and metastasis by targeting matrix metalloproteinases.

articles.title: Endobronchial ultrasound-guided mediastinal biopsies for the diagnosis of mediastinal diseases: A network meta-analysis.
articles.summary: A network meta-analysis shows endobronchial ultrasound-guided biopsies effectively diagnose mediastinal diseases, particularly in lung cancer staging.
